question: Thah-tsuánn ê tsú-kàm-suúi ê thâi-tē ê tō-iâⁿ siōng chhut-hiān siōng chē ê lū-sū sī siáng?
Tī chit danh-toaⁿ ê lōe, ū gōa-chē chi̍p ke-á sī iû chē-ê chhut-la̍i ê chok-chiá phòe-ha̍p? (chhiūⁿ chok-chiá kāi-tāi ko·-ê chhut-la̍i ê chi̍p ke-á)
Chit jī ōe-m̄-sī "The Finals" ê chū-chhiūⁿ-chiá teh chū-chhiūⁿ ê tiān-sì-kio̍k ê miâ-jī, iū-koh ū chi̍t ê im-ga̍k piáu-ián-chiá ê chòe-āu chi̍t ê jī sī "King"?
Tua-jiat 1996 liân, chiàu goân-tāi poat-chhut ê ji̍t-kî lâi kóng, cháiⁿ hē ê tiān-sì-kio̍k chhut-lâi ê pîn-lǜ sī chūiⁿ-iūⁿ?
answer: Tī 1996 nî ê 2 goe̍h, ū sì chhut ê tiān-sì-kio̍k, pun-pia̍t tī 2 goe̍h 1 hō, 8 hō, 15 hō, kap 22 hō hòng-sàng. Chit sì chhut ê tiān-sì-kio̍k chha-put-to lóng sī chi̍t lé-poàⁿ hòng-sàng chi̍t pái, lóng sī chi̍t lé-poàⁿ ê kî-kan.

question: Chiu-su chi̍t-kóa chòe-chok-chiá sī Larry Moskowitz ia̍h-sī Shane Salerno ê só͘-ū chi̍p-chhit ê ga̍k-chok-chiá ê lia̍t-toa̍t.
answer: Al Jarreau "We're In This Love Together"
Luther Vandross " A House Is Not a Home "

question: Tī 1995 nî àⁿ chhut ê lia̍t chhut ê tiān-sī-kio̍k tiong, ū nn̄g-chē huáh-luē sī Michael Lange tō-iǎn ê?

Juah Judith McCreary siat ê só͘-ū ke̍k chhut-lâi ê phoe, chōaⁿ i ê tiān-sì-kio̍k phoe-tōaⁿ-á ê sò͘-liōng tiông-ka 10, "Checkmate" chit khoán phoe ê sin tiān-sì-kio̍k phoe-tōaⁿ-á ê sò͘-liōng ē sī toá-hē?

Tī chit ê chiat-liâu lāi, ū khó-thiaⁿ ê choân-chek kiat-ha̍p ê hong-sek chāi hô-lâng kap siá-chok-jîn tī chiat-liau téng-bīn? (Chit ê chiat-liau lāi, ū khó-thiaⁿ ê choân-chek kiat-ha̍p ê hong-sek chāi hô-lâng kap siá-chok-jîn tī chiat-liau téng-bīn?)
answer: Ū, ū kúi-ā ê choân-chek kiat-ha̍p ê hong-sek. Siōng-kóa-pái ê choán-phòe sī hô-lâng Frederick K. Keller kap siá-chok-jîn Judith McCreary, in chò-hóe chò 2 ê tiâu-bo̍k ("The Highest Bidder" kap "A Time to Kill"). Chi̍t-gōa, kán-ná siá-chok-jîn Natalie Chaidez kap hô-lâng Michael Lange iā chò 2 ê tiâu-bo̍k chò-hóe ("Student Affairs" kap "Young, Beautiful and Dead"), chit-ê sī hui-koân ê choân-chek ha̍p-chok.

question: Tī "Production code" ê keh-á ê lia̍t-la̍k, ē-sī kāng-ê sî-kan phòe-tū ê oân-sêng-sî-á ê oân-sêng-sî-á (Original air date) lia̍t-la̍k ê sî-kan phòe-tū, bē-sī kāng-ê sî-kan phòe-tū ê sî-kan phòe-tū ê oân-sêng-sî-á lia̍t-la̍k ê sî-kan phòe-tū?
answer: Bōe, ê "Production code" bōe siâng-sî-á kāng-ê sî-kan phòe-tū ê oân-sêng-sî-á (Original air date) lia̍t-la̍k ê sî-kan phòe-tū. Chha-ı̄-chòe, ê phìnn-chām "A Time to Kill" (Production code K0519) khòaⁿ-kì ê sî-kan sī 1996-nî 1-go̍eh 4-ji̍t, lēng-gōa ê phìnn-chām "Bad Blood" (Production code K0501) khòaⁿ-kì ê sî-kan sī 1996-nî 1-go̍eh 18-ji̍t, hām i ê Production code hō-bé pí khah chá ê sî-kan.

question: Tī kó-giáⁿ ê siS-chū chè-chō·-bé sī siáⁿ chi̍t ê chāi bīn-tùi i ê khong-khì ji̍t-kî bô-khó-sèⁿ siāng tiōng-iàu ê pēⁿ-ki, ū siāng kē ê sò·-jī chāi-bé, tān-sī chāi chāi si-liàu lāi-bīn khong-khì liáu cha̍p ê pa̍t-ê si-liàu liáu.
